    </video>
    <div class="content">
      <h2 class="h1">
        Flexibility Beyond <br class="br-mobile br-tablet" /> Ordinary
      </h2>
      <p class="paragraph-1">
        The G1 is engineered for maximum flexibility, featuring an extra large
        joint movement angle space and up to 43 Degrees of Freedom (DOF) in the
