        ecosystem, accelerating robotics technology through AI-driven Imitation
        and Reinforcement Learning. Its perception system includes a 3D LiDAR
        and a Depth Camera for 360Â° detection, complemented by a 4 Microphone
        Array for noise and echo cancellation, enabling advanced voice
        interaction.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="shot-section flex-start-row scroll-text-contained">
    <video
      playsinline
      muted
      loop
      preload="metadata"
      width=""
      height=""
      class="media"
